===================
Melodie INSTALL
===================

Required software
-----------------

You need to have the GNUstep core libraries installed in order to
compile and use Melodie. The core packages are, at a minimum:

   * gnustep-make

   * gnustep-base

   * gnustep-gui

   * gnustep-back

   See <http://www.gnustep.org/> for further information.

External dependencies

   * TagLib C binding

   * libmp4v2

Build and Install
-----------------

   Steps to build:

   * make install


Trouble
-------

   Give us feedback! Tell us what you like; tell us what you think
could be better. Send bug reports and patches to <ewasylishen@gmail.com>
